description: Construction of a part four, part twelve storey block of flats fronting Church Street with a row of three storey townhouses and a four storey corner block fronting John Street to provide 70 residential units (Use Class C3), comprising of a tenure of: twenty no. 1-bed units, fifteen no. 2-bed units and 28 no. 3-bed units at London Affordable Rent; three no. 1-bed, three no.2-bed and one no. 3-bed wheelchair accessible M4(3) units at London Affordable Rent; with a central open space and associated landscaping, boundary treatments, three on-site disabled parking spaces and 129 cycle spaces.
